FBIS4-33584 "drlat110_m_94004" FBIS-LAT-94-110 Daily Report 7 Jun 1994 Brazil Last Drug Trafficker Involved in Cocaine Bust Arrested Last Drug Trafficker Involved in Cocaine Bust Arrested PY0706203394 Rio de Janeiro TVE Television in Portuguese 1130 GMT 7 Jun 94 PY0706203394 Rio de Janeiro TVE Television Portuguese BFN [Text] Early this morning the leader of the gang that was transporting 7.5 metric tons [as heard] of cocaine from Tocantins State to Santos, Sao Paulo State, was arrested. Colombian Vicentino Junior had spent two days hiding in the forest along the Tocantins River's banks. Federal Police now are investigating the gang's links with international drug trafficking. The group is believed to be a Brazilian branch of the Cali cartel. The eight Brazilians and three Colombians arrested during the operation will be transferred to Brasilia.
